      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This example is optimized for performance with a recently serviced double VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The powertrain retains its signature linear power delivery and 8,000 RPM redline, supported by a M Variable Differential Lock that provides exceptional corner-exit traction. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including rod bearing clearance checks and refreshed suspension bushings\u2014are excellent. A true enthusiast\u2019s driver, balanced for both technical B-roads and daily engagement.",
